  "notes": "Very wide east-west route (40x9 blocks, 80x18 tiles). Connects New Bark Town (west) to Route 26 (east). The western half is accessible without HMs; the center-east area requires Surf to cross the water and enter Tohjo Falls. The Sandstorm House at tile 33,7 grants TM37 Sandstorm if the player's lead Pokemon has happiness over 150. Bird Keeper Jose offers a Star Piece via phone. Six trainers patrol the route, including Cool Trainer Reena and Bird Keeper Jose with phone rematches. Rare Candy and TM37 Sandstorm (item ball) both sit in the south-center area accessible on foot. Tohjo Falls has two entrances (warps at tiles 26,5 and 36,5)."
